name: Springtime Rose Necklace
description:
This necklace is ever so lovely and feminine. A set of 7 round aqua quartz beads are individually wire wrapped with copper wire and linked with copper chain. At the end of the beaded row is a wire wrapped coral acrylic rose. 

The necklace's total length measures 19 inches, however it can also be adjusted to fit shorter lengths such as 16 inches and 18 inches.

name: Springtime Rose Bracelet
description: Dainty, feminine, and ever so vibrant. This bracelet features aqua colored quartz round stones accompanied with an acrylic coral rose sitting along the center. The bracelet measures 7 inches with a half inch extender and is fastened with a copper "S" hook clasp.

name: Calaveras - Skull Bracelet
description:
This bracelet features a single row of vibrantly colored stone, skull shaped beads. Each bracelet measures 7 inches with an extra half inch extender at the end. The bracelet is fastened with a large copper "S" hook clasp. 

This listing is for one bracelet in your color of choice. The four colors available are blue (turquoise), green, red, and purple.

name: XS/S Vintage Guayabera Dress - Dusty Rose
description:
A little bit about these dresses:

Each is made from a vintage men's guayabera. Guayaberas are generally seen worn by men throughout the Caribbean, Central America, and most notably in Mexico. They are a staple of Mexican and Mexican American culture.

Until now, these wonderfully made shirts with detailed embroidery were predominately enjoyed by only men, however I've designed a way to feminize these shirts and make them accessible to women who love the style as well.

These dresses are meant to be easy fitting and are gathered with an elastic waist and an elastic bust line. All original buttons have been kept on the dress and the button panel has been sewn shut. There also remain 2 original lower pockets, while the original top 2 pockets have been taken away for a better fit.

Again, each dress is made from a vintage guayabera and each will have subtle differences.  This particular dress is made to fit sizes XS-S and will fit the following measurements:

Bust: 28-34 inches
Waist: 20-28 inches
Hip: open
Length: 24 inches

name: Modern Pin Earrings
description:
Modern and minimal.  These earrings are entirely hand crafted and hand forged from copper.  The earrings measure approx. 1.5 inches in length and are incredibly lightweight.  

Sterling silver posts have been soldered onto the copper pins making these earrings suitable for the most sensitive of ears.

name: Copper Hoops
description: Modern, classic, and timeless.  These hoops are a fresh new variation on the classic hoop earring.  This pair is made with hand forged copper and then soldered with sterling silver posts, making them suitable for the most sensitive of ears.  The hoops measure approx. 1.5 inches in diameter.

name: Open Heart Earrings
description:
These cute little heart earrings are entirely made of sterling silver and completely hand crafted. The sterling silver posts make these suitable for even the most sensitive of ears. 

Each hand forged heart measures approx. 12mm when measured at its widest point. These little cuties will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: Copper Lotus Stud Earrings
description:
Find your own little bit of inner peace with these earrings. Each stud has been hand cut from copper and soldered with sterling silver posts (perfect for sensitive ears). Each blooming lotus is individually hand stamped onto copper. 

The copper has been brushed to give it's surface a smooth matte finish. These earrings will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: Copper Key Necklace
description:
A key may represent many things... something that is meant to be kept safe, or even hidden. It may also represent something once kept dear that may longer exist. 

While each necklace has an antiqued, vintage appeal to it, each on is in fact made to order. The necklace is offered in the length of your choice: 16, 18, 20, and 22 inches.

name: Copper MOM Bangle Cuff Bracelet
description:
This bracelet suits the mom with a clean and sophisticated style. Each cuff is hand forged out of 100% copper and features the simple, yet loving inscription of "MOM" along the outer surface. This bracelet is brushed to give it a smooth matted finish. Each letter is individually stamped therefore variations on letter alignment is normal.

Because the bracelet is made of 100% copper, keep in mind that the metal may react with skin. A clear wax sealant has been applied to this ring to minimize the reaction as well as general oxidization, however the wax may wear off over time. The reaction to skin is generally harmless and results in a greenish/grayish tint on the skin that can easily be washed off.

name: Dia de los Muertos Necklace
description:
This necklace features the solitary, and somewhat ghostly image of a skull.  This necklace is the perfect accessory for the fall! 

The coin shaped pendant is hand crafted from fine silver and hangs from an 18 inch sterling plated chain.  The pendant has been hand burnished and slightly oxidized to bring out all of it's wonderfully sublime details.

name: Sugar Skull Wristlet Clutch
description:
This accessory features the wonderful imagery of vibrantly colored sugar skulls; a traditional staple for any Dia de los Muertos celebration.  

The clutch features pockets and compartments necessary for all of your essentials.  Beneath it's velcro flap is a bill fold, two card slots, and a large zipper pocket.  A detachable lobster clasp fastened to a strap sits along the side, making it the perfect place to hold a set of keys.  

Not too big, not too small, the clutch measures at 9 inches wide, and 5 inches high.  There's actually a place for everything, and everything actually has a place.  After this nifty little accessory, you may quickly get rid of that over-sized purse!

name: Dia de los Muertos Ring
description:
This festive little ring features a solitary, and somewhat ghostly image of a skull along a coin shaped surface.  Each surface is hand stamped and hand burnished with the skeletal image.

The coin shaped surface of the ring is comprised of fine silver, while the band is constructed out of sterling silver.  Each ring is individually hand crafted to order.

name: Frida Kitchen Apron - Half
description:
This vibrant apron combines the wonderful imagery of Frida Kahlo in an idyllic, surreal garden.  In it you'll find fruit, monkeys, palm, parrots, corazons, and of course Frida herself.  The apron is accented with dusty teal and turquoise trim.

The apron measures 24 inches wide while it's ties measure 72 inches from end to end, making the apron suitable for all sizes.  For added function, a pocket sits off to one side, while the opposite side features a sewn in turquoise towel.

name: Josephine Apron II
description:
This is a redesign of my very popular first Josephine Apron. This half apron is made with a combination of 100% cotton fabric and yellow linen. The skirt of the apron has a tremendous amount of flare, ruffle, and texture. A handful of bustles have also been added along the top layer of the apron topped with hand sewn wooden buttons. 

The width of the apron's skirt measures at 21 inches, while the ties measure at 69 inches from end to end.

name: Birdcage Full Apron - Large
description:
Contrasting black and white silhouettes with splashes of teal, burgundy, and olive give the apron a delightful, vintage appeal.  This full apron features a bit of flexible ruffling along the top for a flattering fit.  Two pockets are also featured along the front of the skirt.  

This apron is perfect for fuller and taller figures.  The apron measures 34 inches from top bib to bottom of the skirt.  The waist band measures 28 inches while the waist ties measure 80 inches from end to end.

name: Copper FOREVER Ring
description:
This lovely ring features the inscription of "FOREVER" along the inside. Each letter is individually hand stamped and variations on letter alignment is normal. The simple style makes this ring suitable for both men and women and features a smooth matte finish both inside and out. The ring also makes for a unique substitute for an otherwise traditional wedding band. 

The ring measures 5mm in width, and 1mm in thickness. Because this ring is made of 100% copper, keep in mind that the metal may react with your skin. A clear wax sealant has been applied to this ring to minimize the reaction as well as general oxidization, however the wax may wear off over time. The reaction to skin is generally harmless and results in a greenish/grayish tint on the skin that can easily be washed off. 

Each ring is hand crafted from copper metal, and made to order. If you are unsure of your size, refer to the last image to get an idea of sizing. The copper band has been soldered with sterling silver and does feature a tiny silver sliver at the seam. 

This ring will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: Simplicity Band - She
description:
This ring is simply timeless. It's clean and classic design is sure to gain the admiration of just about anyone.

Each ring is handcrafted out of solid sterling silver and is hand burnished to give it a smooth mirror finish.

This band is made in the size of your choice and measures 5mm wide and 1mm in thickness. The last photo in this set features this ring along side the "Him" version, making these rings lovely options as wedding bands ("Him" version not included).

name: Simplicity Band - Him
description:
This ring is simply timeless.  It's clean and classic design is sure to gain the admiration of just about anyone.  

Each ring is handcrafted out of solid sterling silver and is hand burnished to give it a smooth mirror finish.  

This band is made in the size of your choice and measures 8mm wide and 1mm in thickness.  The last photo in this set features this ring along side the "She" version, making these rings lovely options as wedding bands ("She" version not included).

name: Two Turtle Dove Earrings
description:
Sweet, Simple and dainty.  These little dove earrings will quickly become your favorite pair.  

The earrings measure at about 1 inch in length and hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Sparrow Earrings
description:
Whimsical with a dash of the dramatic.  These lovely earrings depict the image of a sparrow in mid flight.  

The earrings measure at about 1.5 inches in length and the metal sparrows hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Butterfly Earrings
description:
Sweet, Simple and dainty. These little butterfly earrings will quickly become your favorite pair.  The metal butterflies appear to be softly fluttering just below your earlobe.  

The earrings measure at about 1 inch in length and hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Attic Key Earrings
description:
These keys are slightly different than the other keys... Made for that one special attic door.  These delicate pewter keys make for the perfect everyday accessory.

These keys hang about 1 inch in length and hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Eiffel Tower Earrings
description: Sweet, dainty and a little bit of oh, la, la.  These earrings measure at approx. 1 inch in length and hang from silver plated french ear hooks.

name: Mini Owl Earrings
description:
These little owls are ever so cute!  They've got a lovely amount of detail, and yet are petite enough to comfortably wear everyday.  For the woodsy, naturalist type, these can easily become your favorite pair of earrings.  

The earrings measure at about 1 inch in length and hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Key Earrings
description:
These cute little earrings are ever so delicate and lovely.  Perfect for those romantics who love a dash of mystery.  

These little keys are very lightweight and hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Orchard Earrings
description:
These earrings are perfect for any nature lover.  The short design of the tree remind me of trees from either an apple or peach orchard.  Suddenly the smell of fresh fruit comes to mind!  

These earrings measure about 1 inch in length and hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Mini Leaf earrings
description:
Cute, delicate, and dainty.  The petite silver leaves feature lovely flowing lines throughout.  Since making these, I've kept a pair for myself, and they've quickly become my favorite go-to pair of earrings and I wear them nearly everyday.  

These earrings measure about 1 inch in length and hang from silver plated ear wires.

name: Places of Interest Necklace - Small
description:
Oh, the places you'll go! For some, a place is more than just hometown glory... a place can bring up nostalgic memories of childhood and of loved ones from long ago. It can also be the origins of a fantastic getaway from years past or a romantic honeymoon. Then again, a place can be somewhere you long to someday visit, anxiously awaiting to be crossed off of your bucket list.

In this necklace, these places will always remain close to you. Each pendant is carefully handmade and cast in resin with a specific place in mind. All images were created from vintage maps and atlases predating 1985 and no two necklaces are ever the same. In some cases, many of these places don't even exist anymore (i.e. Leningrad, Bombay).

Each pendant hangs from a silver tone bail and off a 17 inch chain. Each necklace is fastened with a silver plated lobster clasp and findings. Each pendant measures about 3/4 inches in length. While these pendants are water resistant, they aren't entirely waterproof. Please refrain from wearing while swimming or showering.

Many cities and regions are readily available, however if you don't see your place among available listings, email INFO@B-LINKDESIGN.COM to add your place for purchase.

This necklace will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: Loteria Necklace
description:
If you are familiar with Mexican traditions and pastimes, then you're familiar with Loteria.  For those unaware, Loteria is very much like BINGO, except instead of calling out letters and numbers, characters/icons are called out (and in some cases riddles) from a deck of loteria cards.  When a character on your card is called, you place a bean over it and continue to try and connect a line or group of spaces... much like BINGO. 

Several of these iconic images from loteria cards have been transformed into lovely pendants.  Each pendant is handcrafted and cast in resin and hangs from a silver tone bail off a 17 inch chain.  The entire necklace is fastened with a silver plated lobster clasp and findings.  While these pendants are water resistant, they are not entirely waterproof.  Please refrain from swimming or showering with the necklace.  

Many icons have been created and are readily available, but not all loteria characters are currently available.  If you don't see your preferred icon listed, please email INFO@B-LINKDESIGN.COM to have your character created and added to the list for purchase.

name: Bedknobs and Broomsticks Bracelet
description:
This fun and whimsical bracelet features delightful pewter charms transcending time and space.  In it, you'll find woodland creatures, antique keys, trees and even the Eiffel tower.  The bracelet also features faceted jade gemstones in aqua, tangerine, burgundy, and lime.  The entire bracelet is fastened together with a large rustic silver tone toggle clasp and measures 8 inches in length.  

This item will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: Owl Necklace
description:
This necklace features a cute little owl perched curiously at the center of the pendant.  The pendant has been individually burnished to give it a mirror finish and has been slightly oxidized to bring out the details within the owl.

The pendant's diameter measures at 5/8 inch and sits along an 18 inch sterling silver chain. The entire necklace is held together with a sterling silver spring clasp and sterling silver findings

name: Owl Ring
description: A perfect companion to one of my other pieces: Owl Necklace The coin shaped face measures at 5/8 inch and sits along a sterling silver band in the size of your choice.

name: Polyhedron Necklace - Red
description: This necklace combines several of my favorite elements; minimalism, modernism, and geometry.  The focal point of this piece is a 14 sided, wooded, red polyhedron.  The wooden polyhedron measures at about 15mm in width and sits at the center of a 17in silver plated chain.  All other findings in this necklace are also silver plated.

name: Polyhedron Necklace - Orange
description: This necklace combines several of my favorite elements; minimalism, modernism, and geometry. The focal point of this piece is a 14 sided, wooded, orange polyhedron. The wooden polyhedron measures at about 11mm in width and sits at the center of a 17in silver plated chain. All other findings in this necklace are also silver plated.

name: Lascaux Necklace
description:
This necklace is bold and not for the faint of heart.  The double stranded necklace is made with a combination of large wooden teal beads and white porcelain disks nestled in between.  There is a great amount of texture to this piece as well as each disk is irregularly shaped and vertical notches grace the surface of each wooden bead.  

The design of this necklace hints to a primordial era.  The inner layer of the necklace measures at 22 inches, while the outer layer drapes just below at 26 inches.  Due to the wooden and porcelain materials, this seemingly grand necklace is very lightweight and easy to wear.  The entire piece is fastened with a toggle clasp.

name: Turquoise Butterfly Earrings
description: These earrings are bright and ever so adorable! The butterflies are made out of turquoise colored howlite and are accompanied by a small sterling silver bead sitting at it's top. Each butterfly is individually wire wrapped and hang about 1 inch below silver ear wires.

name: First Love Necklace
description:
This necklace is sweet token to show one's loving affection. The disk shaped pendant displays the solitary imprint of a heart. The handmade pendant was hand stamped and created out of fine silver. It measures at 1/2 inch and has been hand burnished to give it's surface a mirror finish and it has been slightly oxidized to bring out the details within the heart. 

The pendant hangs from an 18 inch sterling silver chain and is fastened with sterling silver findings. This item will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: Starry Night Ring
description:
I used a combination of textures and images on fine silver to emulate the style demonstrated by Vincent Van Gogh in his piece, "Starry Night". When creating this ring I wanted to make sure there was a sense of movement along with the presence of celestial objects. 

The coin shaped face was created by layering two silver disks. The larger base disk features flowing lines while the smaller one sitting off to it's side is imprinted with a single star. The entire ring, including it's sterling silver band, has been oxidized to bring out the details from within. Depending on your skin's personal acidity level, some of the oxidization may wear off over time, however the oxidization along the surface of the disks should remain unaffected.

name: Rustic Sweetheart Ring
description:
This ring features a handmade sterling silver band with a solid rustic heart sitting at it's center. The solid heart was also hand forged, made of fine silver, and measures at just under a half inch at it's widest point. The ring has been slightly oxidized to bring out the textured details within the heart. 

The ring's modern and simplistic design makes it ideal for everyday wear. Each ring is custom made in the size of your choice and will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: As You Wish Ring
description:
This ring was inspired by one of my favorite movies... The Princess Bride. Inscribed along the inside of this seemingly simple band is the phrase "As You Wish." This line is quoted by the movie's hero, Wesley throughout the film.

The ring is made of sterling silver and has a bit of a rustic feel to it, as if Wesley himself made the ring as a special gift to Buttercup. The thin band measures about 1/8 inch in width. This ring is made to order and in the size of your choice

name: Mothers Cross Necklace
description:
For the mom that has just about everything. This personalized cross is sure to be a treasured keepsake for years to come. Each fine silver cross is individually hand made and features the engraving of "MOM" on the back. Since each cross is hand made, other words of comparable size may be substituted and engraved on the back. Please email all inquiries to info@b-linkdesign.com

Each cross measures at just under one inch in length and is slightly oxidized to bring out the details of the design and texture. The pendant hangs on an 18 inch sterling silver chain and is fastened with sterling silver findings. This necklace will arrive to you boxed and ready for gift giving.

name: Forever Ring
description:
This ring is a simple reminder that your love is eternal, wherever you may find that love.  This ring is made of solid sterling silver and measures 1/8 inch in width.  This piece has a bit of a rustic feel to it, as the surface has been slightly hammered for added texture.  

Inscribed along the inside of the ring is the word FOREVER.  The ring's classic, unisex design makes it suitable for both men and women alike. 

Each ring is individually handcrafted and made in the size of your choice.  Other phrases comparable in length to FOREVER can also be inscribed, please email these inquiries to brandy@b-linkdesign.com

name: The Birds Necklace
description:
This necklace is named after the Alfred Hitchcock cinematic thriller, THE BIRDS.  While the pendant does not emanate the menacing terror of birds, it does resemble the director's silohette at the beginning of "Alfred Hitchcock Presents."

The pendant is individually made of fine silver and measures at 1/2 inch in diameter.  The petite pendant hangs off of an 18 inch sterling silver chain and is fastened with sterling silver findings.

name: Sparrow Necklace
description:
This pendant depicts the peaceful image of a little sparrow quietly perched on a branch, making this the perfect token for your favorite nature lover.  The pendant is individually handmade out of fine silver and slightly oxidized to bring out it's details.   

The pendant's diameter measures at 5/8 inch and sits along an 18 inch sterling silver chain. The entire necklace is held together with a sterling silver spring clasp and sterling silver findings.

name: Rose Blossom Ring
description:
This ring is boldly understated, if that makes any sense.  While it posses plenty of texture and dimension, there still remains a simple and elegant quality within the piece.  

The sterling silver blossom sits along a simple handcrafted sterling silver band.  The blossom measures approx. 1/2 inch and the ring is made in the size of your choice.

name: Juliet's Ring
description:
"That which we call a rose by any other name would smell as sweet?" Juliet's clasic quote from Shakespeare was the inspiration behind this ring. 

A delicate imprint of a blooming rose sits at the center of a handmade fine silver disk measuring 1/2 inch in diameter.  The sterling silver band, is also hand forged, and lightly hand hammered.  This sterling silver ring will arrive to you in the size of your choice.

name: This Too Shall Pass Ring
description: This ring serves as a little reminder of better things to come. The coin shaped surface features the phrase "This Too Shall Pass" along its perimeter. This sterling silver ring is individually made in the size of your choice.

name: Briar Rose Ring
description:
This sweet little ring features a detailed blossoming rose sitting along the center of a sterling silver band. The rose was handcrafted out of fine silver, while the band was handcrafted out of sterling silver. The rose has been hand burnished to give it a mirror shine and then oxidized to bring out the details of every petal. 

Each ring is made to order and in the size of your choice.

name: Rocket Necklace
description:
As a kid, I always wanted to be an astronaut.  The simple silhouette of a rocket blasting off often brings back memories of wonderment and fantasy.  This necklace is sure to be the perfect gift for your favorite sci-fi enthusiast.  

The rocket pendant is individually stamped and made of fine silver, measuring at 1/2 inch in diameter.  The petite pendant hangs off of an 18 inch sterling silver chain and is fastened with sterling silver findings.

name: Le Petite Personalized Necklace
description:
This necklace is dainty, light and feminine.  This listing is for one necklace featuring a handmade fine silver pendant stamped with the letter of your choice.  Each pendant is also accompanied with a petite freshwater pearl.  

This necklace makes for a great gift for all occasions from first communions, to birthdays, to bridal party favors.  

Each necklace features an 18 inch sterling silver chain and is fastened with a sterling silver spring clasp.  All other findings in this necklace are also made with sterling silver.

name: Bicycle Necklace
description:
The perfect item for your favorite cyclist. The coin shaped pendant features a hand stamped imprint of an old fashioned cruiser bicycle. 

The pendant's diameter measures at 5/8 inch and sits along an 18 inch sterling silver chain.

name: Crochet Tam
description:
This is a must have accessory for just about anyone and is one size fits most (fitting heads 20-25 inches).  At it's widest point, the hat measures at 26 inches in circumference, leaving plenty of room for tucking hair back or even tucking back dreadlocks.  

The hat's open stitching allows it to be comfortably worn in both cooler and warmer months and is made to order in the color of your choice.  The colors featured in the sample photos are Teal, Fig, and Lemongrass.  All other color options can be seen in the last photo.

The hat is made of an acrylic/wool blend yarn and is machine washable, however hand washing or dry cleaning is best.
